                        <p><strong>Adresse:</strong> Kästobel 13<br>87509 Immenstadt</p>
                        
                        <div class="contact-details">
                            <p><strong>Handy:</strong> <a href="tel:+491604996655">0160 4996655</a></p>
                        </div>
                        
